Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人注意！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始我将对特洛斯特区夺还作战进行说明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要从向大家介绍这位士兵开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦·耶格尔训练兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我们秘密研制的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人化活体试验中的成功案例
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身为巨人的他将会举起前门附近那块巨石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它搬运至被破坏的大门处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后堵住破洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位的任务是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他搬运岩石的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护他免受别的巨人伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当此次作战成功之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类将第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功地从巨人手中夺回自己的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和人类至今为止被夺去的东西相比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定只是一次微不足道的小小胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一小步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于人类来说却是进击的一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦  你不认识我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是三笠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快闪开  阿克曼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是个脑子很笨的普通巨人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战计划有变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回收耶格尔之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要保护他不受巨人伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对人类来说是贵重的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能轻易放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让  为什么不用立体机动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装置发生故障了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想办法解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不能扔下艾伦不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人越来越多  会全军覆没的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后脑到颈部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长1米  宽10厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦  回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要踏出墙外一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是地狱般的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想前往外面的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我生在了这个世界上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:45.01,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,原始的欲望\N{\fs-2}—特洛斯特区攻防战{\fs-1}⑨—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐  我怎么能拖他们后腿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能…有救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长  到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只剩下我们两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时先退到岩石那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有5只巨人  从大门方向过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会一直等到巨人都走光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是机动装置…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑  偏偏在这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让  冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  别给我们添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账  为什么扳机这么硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话应该是我问你吧  快点跳走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱来的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不相信自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦他战胜了自己的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在正在努力完成自己的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后只要掩护艾伦至大门处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我死守！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使要用我们的命来交换
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要保护艾伦到大门处！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能让巨人接近他！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻碍他们的行动  掩护艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个人给我去艾伦的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令！明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米塔比班…  你们在做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人们根本不理我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只有尽量接近来吸引它们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边啊  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不转过来的话我就把刀插进你们的屁股里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了  有两只上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起来  快往建筑物那边跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会  降落到地面上无异于自杀行为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有马和建筑物就没法战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  现在只有这种方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟紧米塔比班！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿明  我们也快行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来  到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛要四分五裂一般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠  阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方走来走去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会成为巨人的饵食的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快点过来啊  你这个傻大个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米塔比！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦为什么还想前往外面的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所有人从出生的那一刻开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:11:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管有多么强大的敌人来阻碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧的水也好  冰冻的大地也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够看到那些的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是这个世界上最自由的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了自由我将不惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管世界多么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管世界多么残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要挡着路！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧  艾伦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的牺牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有白费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战胜了巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到了黄色烟雾弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战好像成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧派遣援军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出精锐班
